      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should check but it's like 2am and my clinic is closed. i'm just so miserable and i've heard people take it all the time. is it actually dangerous or is it just something doctors say to be extra cautious? like i've already taken a tiny bit and i felt fine, i just really need to know if a standard dose is going to cause issues or if i'm overreacting.",
