      "content": "the saline rinse isn't really doing anything and i'm honestly getting a fever too. i just really need the pressure to stop so i can rest. i read online that some people say its fine in the second trimester because the organs are already formed. if i just take one pill, a normal dose, what's the worst that could happen? i just need some reassurance that a single dose isn't going to cause a problem.",
